{/* HERO */}

Request Transfer Out

Use this form to request the release of your Nevada real estate license to a new brokerage. We’ll prepare the broker release and coordinate the transfer.

{/* EXPLAINER */}

What You’ll Need

  • Your full name, contact info, and NV license number
  • New brokerage name and broker’s contact email
  • Preferred effective date and any special instructions

How It Works

  1. Submit the request with your new brokerage details.
  2. We issue the broker release and (if selected) send a DocuSign packet.
  3. After the state processes the change, we’ll confirm completion.
Typical processing time depends on the state and responsiveness of all parties. We’ll keep you posted if anything else is needed.

Need Assistance?

If you have a closing pending or a unique situation, let us know so we can time your transfer accordingly.

Email: support@your-domain.com
Phone: (000) 000-0000

{/* FORM */}
